{"tid":640913,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實如果真係咁愛 又點會分手","createTime":"2018-04-24T15:34:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T09:10:25.000Z","uid":157363,"like":176,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"50566cc27506f9c0d8974293a81b24c5284b8500","tid":640913,"uid":157363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T15:34:03.000Z","msg":"成日口口聲聲話你係全世界最愛<br />\n其實如果佢真係咁愛你<br />\n唔會令你有傷心流淚嘅機會<br />\n唔會令你有亂諗野嘅機會<br />\n唔會令你有想離開嘅理由<br />\n<br />\n所以其實最後選擇分手<br />\n都係因為大家唔夠愛對方or唔識愛對方啊<br />\n咩攰喇心累了都係bullshit<br />\n淡左就淡左啦 <br />\n唔夠愛咪搞到分手囉<br />\n仲可以咁厚面皮話自己好愛嘅人都唔知咩心態<br />\n<br />\n別傻了 別傻了<br />\n我不會喜歡你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4306da692e2409fc6516c1ccde834b547ebc4a68","tid":640913,"uid":182911,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T15:41:50.000Z","msg":"唔好再諗啦 人地心已經無左你 再諗都係浪費時間<br />\n諗下點樣將自己升級好過<br />\n夜啦 早d訓啦"},{"pid":"8a252ef61df7d3ad18d77da105eee7e093ded6b1","tid":640913,"uid":157363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4306da692e2409fc6516c1ccde834b547ebc4a68","tid":640913,"uid":182911,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T15:41:50.000Z","msg":"唔好再諗啦 人地心已經無左你 再諗都係浪費時間<br />\n諗下點樣將自己升級好過<br />\n夜啦 早d訓啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T15:59:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 憤怒會激勵自己變得更好"},{"pid":"bee026adac41feb57d470be64297c36a380a49c7","tid":640913,"uid":148185,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T16:02:48.000Z","msg":"夠鐘了"},{"pid":"6255582f8af3629bfd9e35d6edf532cec4c0d942","tid":640913,"uid":117497,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T16:05:59.000Z","msg":"想有人愛，所以先愛人，最後都係唔愛了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a7a3235dda5bf4ad68f8efd05a2dc2346c3034f","tid":640913,"uid":178333,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"50566cc27506f9c0d8974293a81b24c5284b8500","tid":640913,"uid